videos.headline: Colorado's trickeration for  28-yard gain.
videos.description: Colorado uses a reverse pass for a big 28-yard completion to Laviska Shenault Jr.

videos.headline: Colorado's Montez tosses a 3-yard TD
videos.description: Steven Montez passes to an open Jay MacIntyre for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Laviska Shenault Jr. drags Nebraska defenders for a TD
videos.description: Laviska Shenault Jr. plows through Nebraska's defense to score a 3-yard Colorado touchdown.

videos.headline: Nebraska's Martinez eludes defender and runs for 41-yard TD
videos.description: Adrian Martinez escapes a Colorado defender and sprints for a 41-yard Nebraska touchdown.

videos.headline: Davis' 8-yard TD runs ties game for Nebraska
videos.description: Alex Davis' 8-yard touchdown run brings Nebraska square with Colorado.

videos.headline: Martinez fakes out Colorado on 3-yard TD
videos.description: After being down 14-0, Nebraska takes the lead with a 3-yard touchdown run by Adrian Martinez.

videos.headline: Martinez slings deep TD to extend Nebraska's lead
videos.description: Adrian Martinez shows off his arm with a deep 57-yard touchdown pass to JD Spielman to increase Nebraska's lead.

videos.headline: Montez cuts Colorado deficit with 8-yard TD pass
videos.description: Steve Montez and JD MacIntyre connect on a touchdown for the second time to bring Colorado within one of Nebraska.

videos.headline: Colorado D comes up big with 4th-down stop
videos.description: LB Nate Landman slashes in and makes big tackle on fourth down, giving the ball back to Colorado.

videos.headline: Nebraska Martinez picked off by Colorado
videos.description: Colorado LB Nate Landman makes another play by intercepting Nebraska's Adrian Martinez.

videos.headline: Colorado takes the lead on Montez's 40-yard TD pass
videos.description: Steven Montez throws deep to Laviska Shenault Jr., who works his way into the end zone for a 40-yard touchdown to give Colorado a lead late.

videos.headline: Colorado stops last-second heave to clinch win
videos.description: Nebraska backup QB Andrew Brunch throws up a last second heave, but it falls incomplete as Colorado spoils Scott Frost's debut.
